March 1, 2026</b>, devices using <b style=3D"font-family: Segoe UI Semibold=
, SegoeUISemibold, Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, A=
rial, sans-serif;font-weight: 600">
Exchange ActiveSync (EAS)</b> versions lower than 16.1 will no longer be ab=
le to connect to Exchange Online. EAS 16.1 was introduced in June 2016 and =
provides enhanced compatibility and security.</p>
<p style=3D"color: #11100f;font-family: Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Roboto, &quot;He=
lvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;padding-top: 0;paddi=
