<b style=3D"font-family: Segoe UI Semibold, SegoeUISemibold, Segoe UI, Sego=
eUI, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight: 600=
">Who is affected:</b> Organizations using mobile devices with native email=
 apps to access Exchange Online mailboxes via
 EAS protocol. Apple devices added support for EAS 16.1 in iOS 10 and are u=
nlikely to be affected. The Gmail app and Samsung Mail will have updated ve=
rsions available before the deadline. For other apps you should contact you=
r device or application vendor if
 they are using EAS versions lower than 16.1.&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"color: #11100f;font-family: Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Roboto, &quot;He=
lvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;padding-top: 0;paddi=
